			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "<anim name='Emoji_Stork' nonBlocking='true'/> I weigh a little more than the average newborn baby. <break size='1.7'/> But <anim name='Greetings_02' nonBlocking='true'/> I'm not quite as cuddly.",
